thread.title: China May factory growth at 8-mth high, trade fears loom

title: China May factory growth at 8-mth high, trade fears loom
text:
China May factory growth at 8-mth high, trade fears loom 11:56am BST - 01:25
China's vast manufacturing sector grew at the fastest pace in eight months in May, blowing past expectations and easing concerns about an economic slowdown even as risks from trade tensions with the United States and a crackdown on debt point to a bumpy ride ahead. Ciara Lee reports
